<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-77-1000 </DOCNO><TEXT>A wide range of the most commonly used incineration systems and basicselectioning criteria, according to type of waste to be incinerated,is submitted to the attention of design specialists, technicians andoperators. A brief outline of the Italian situation, with regard to wasteincineration, and to the trend in the most representative foreign countriesis given.</TEXT></DOC>